ARCH: 0.4
CONT: db
PATH: broker/src/db
DEP: identity
DESC: SQLite persistence — schema, migrations, repository pattern for all data access

MOD: db
  FILE: mod.rs
  OWN: database-connection; sqlite-handle; open; open_memory; migrate
  BND: Connection management and migration only — no queries beyond DDL

MOD: schema
  FILE: schema.rs
  OWN: migrations; table-definitions; ensure_schema
  BND: Schema DDL only — no DML queries

MOD: repository
  FILE: repository.rs
  OWN: Repository; PendingMessage; register_project; register_agent; agent_exists; project_exists; ensure_channel; channel_exists; is_cross_project_allowed; seed_cross_project_default; get_subscribers; subscribe; unsubscribe; insert_message; record_pending; record_delivered; drain_pending; peek_pending; cleanup; find_agents_by_name
  BND: Pure persistence — all SQL lives here, no business logic
  DEP: db/db; identity/secret
